job.title: NEEPCO Officer Recruitment 2021 – Apply Online for Various  Vacancies in Delhi
job.body:
Total Vacancies: Various

Name of the Posts:

  • Director(Technical)

Description

New Central Government Jobs for Engineers has been published by North Eastern Electric Power Corporation Limited for the vacancies of Director(Technical). If you are searching for a government job in New Delhi then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Director(Technical), from 12.05.2021, and till 22.07.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.


Application fee

  • Mode of application is Online

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Director(Technical) vacancies in New Delhi, your Engineering, MBA/Post Graduation Diploma must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 12.05.2021.
  •  Last date to apply in these posts is 22.07.2021

Age Limit Criteria

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 45  years old. 

NEEPCO Director(Technical) Pay Scale

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 180000-340000/-.

How to apply for NEEPCO Officer Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Director(Technical). Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of NEEPCO and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by NEEPCO.
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
